data.description: Large Lakeside home full of unique features for the area. This home features 4 generous sized bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, updated hardwood flooring throughout the main floor, a large front porch, 2 stairwells, a full basement with a bar, and an oversized 1 stall garage. The home is located just a short distance to Lakeside's shopping district, Great Lakes Marina, Muskegon Lake, and Lake Michigan. Immediate possession - do not miss this home. Call today for your private showing! Buyer and buyer's agent to verify all information.
